{"snp4.13:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.13 ","snp4.13:0.2":"Mahabyuhasutta ","snp4.13:1.1":"“Ye kecime ditthiparibbasana, ","snp4.13:1.2":"Idameva saccanti vivadayanti; ","snp4.13:1.3":"Sabbeva te nindamanvanayanti, ","snp4.13:1.4":"Atho pasamsampi labhanti tattha”. ","snp4.13:2.1":"“Appanhi etam na alam samaya, ","snp4.13:2.2":"Duve vivadassa phalani brumi; ","snp4.13:2.3":"Etampi disva na vivadayetha, ","snp4.13:2.4":"Khemabhipassam avivadabhumim”. ","snp4.13:3.1":"“Ya kacima sammutiyo puthujja, ","snp4.13:3.2":"Sabbava eta na upeti vidva; ","snp4.13:3.3":"Anupayo so upayam kimeyya, ","snp4.13:3.4":"Ditthe sute khantimakubbamano”. ","snp4.13:4.1":"“Siluttama sannamenahu suddhim, ","snp4.13:4.2":"Vatam samadaya upatthitase; ","snp4.13:4.3":"Idheva sikkhema athassa suddhim, ","snp4.13:4.4":"Bhavupanita kusalavadana. ","snp4.13:5.1":"Sace cuto silavatato hoti, ","snp4.13:5.2":"Pavedhati kamma viradhayitva; ","snp4.13:5.3":"Pajappati patthayati ca suddhim, ","snp4.13:5.4":"Satthava hino pavasam gharamha. ","snp4.13:6.1":"Silabbatam vapi pahaya sabbam, ","snp4.13:6.2":"Kammanca savajjanavajjametam; ","snp4.13:6.3":"Suddhim asuddhinti apatthayano, ","snp4.13:6.4":"Virato care santimanuggahaya. ","snp4.13:7.1":"Tamupanissaya jigucchitam va, ","snp4.13:7.2":"Atha vapi dittham va sutam mutam va; ","snp4.13:7.3":"Uddhamsara suddhimanutthunanti, ","snp4.13:7.4":"Avitatanhase bhavabhavesu. ","snp4.13:8.1":"Patthayamanassa hi jappitani, ","snp4.13:8.2":"Pavedhitam vapi pakappitesu; ","snp4.13:8.3":"Cutupapato idha yassa natthi, ","snp4.13:8.4":"Sa kena vedheyya kuhim va jappe”. ","snp4.13:9.1":"“Yamahu dhammam paramanti eke, ","snp4.13:9.2":"Tameva hinanti panahu anne; ","snp4.13:9.3":"Sacco nu vado katamo imesam, ","snp4.13:9.4":"Sabbeva hime kusalavadana”. ","snp4.13:10.1":"“Sakanhi dhammam paripunnamahu, ","snp4.13:10.2":"Annassa dhammam pana hinamahu; ","snp4.13:10.3":"Evampi viggayha vivadayanti, ","snp4.13:10.4":"Sakam sakam sammutimahu saccam. ","snp4.13:11.1":"Parassa ce vambhayitena hino, ","snp4.13:11.2":"Na koci dhammesu visesi assa; ","snp4.13:11.3":"Puthu hi annassa vadanti dhammam, ","snp4.13:11.4":"Nihinato samhi dalham vadana. ","snp4.13:12.1":"Saddhammapujapi nesam tatheva, ","snp4.13:12.2":"Yatha pasamsanti sakayanani; ","snp4.13:12.3":"Sabbeva vada tathiya bhaveyyum, ","snp4.13:12.4":"Suddhi hi nesam paccattameva. ","snp4.13:13.1":"Na brahmanassa paraneyyamatthi, ","snp4.13:13.2":"Dhammesu niccheyya samuggahitam; ","snp4.13:13.3":"Tasma vivadani upativatto, ","snp4.13:13.4":"Na hi setthato passati dhammamannam. ","snp4.13:14.1":"Janami passami tatheva etam, ","snp4.13:14.2":"Ditthiya eke paccenti suddhim; ","snp4.13:14.3":"Addakkhi ce kinhi tumassa tena, ","snp4.13:14.4":"Atisitva annena vadanti suddhim. ","snp4.13:15.1":"Passam naro dakkhati namarupam, ","snp4.13:15.2":"Disvana va nassati tanimeva; ","snp4.13:15.3":"Kamam bahum passatu appakam va, ","snp4.13:15.4":"Na hi tena suddhim kusala vadanti. ","snp4.13:16.1":"Nivissavadi na hi subbinayo, ","snp4.13:16.2":"Pakappitam ditthi purakkharano; ","snp4.13:16.3":"Yam nissito tattha subham vadano, ","snp4.13:16.4":"Suddhim vado tattha tathaddasa so. ","snp4.13:17.1":"Na brahmano kappamupeti sankha, ","snp4.13:17.2":"Na ditthisari napi nanabandhu; ","snp4.13:17.3":"Natva ca so sammutiyo puthujja, ","snp4.13:17.4":"Upekkhati uggahananti manne. ","snp4.13:18.1":"Vissajja ganthani munidha loke, ","snp4.13:18.2":"Vivadajatesu na vaggasari; ","snp4.13:18.3":"Santo asantesu upekkhako so, ","snp4.13:18.4":"Anuggaho uggahananti manne. ","snp4.13:19.1":"Pubbasave hitva nave akubbam, ","snp4.13:19.2":"Na chandagu nopi nivissavadi; ","snp4.13:19.3":"Sa vippamutto ditthigatehi dhiro, ","snp4.13:19.4":"Na lippati loke anattagarahi. ","snp4.13:20.1":"Sa sabbadhammesu visenibhuto, ","snp4.13:20.2":"Yam kinci dittham va sutam mutam va; ","snp4.13:20.3":"Sa pannabharo muni vippamutto, ","snp4.13:20.4":"Na kappiyo nuparato na patthiyo”ti. ","snp4.13:20.5":"Mahabyuhasuttam terasamam. "}